== Initial Installation
source env.sh
./build-docker-image.sh
./build-qemu-image.sh
./compile-kernel.sh
./compile-monitor.sh
./compile-nvme-tools.sh
./compile-qemu.sh
./compile-tests.sh

./run-sanity.sh

== Running QEMU
./run-qemu.sh
    - Accessible via ssh @ port 2222 username=esd password=esd
    - Accessible via vnc @ port 5900
    - eVSSIM API @ http port 2003
    - CTRL+C To stop

    - While QEMU is running, the following scripts are available
        ./enter-ssh.sh - Enter using SSH into the running QEMU virtual machine (Guest)
        ./enter-docker.sh - Enter into the running QEMU container image (Host)


== Running docker
./run-bash.sh - Run bash inside an empty docker
./runbash-chrooted.sh - Run bash inside the image of the QEMU guest